title: Grateful Dead Live at Meadowlands Arena on 1983-04-17
description:
Set 1

Touch Of Gray-> Little Red Rooster, Dupree's Diamond Blues-> Beat It On Down The Line, Must Have Been the Roses, Cassidy, Big RR Blues, Brother Esau, Peggy-O, Let It Grow, Might As Well

Set 2

Help On The Way-> Slipknot!-> Franklin's Tower-> Women Are Smarter-> Playin' In The Band-> Drums-> Love The One You're With*-> The Wheel-> Playin' In The Band-> Throwing Stones-> Not Fade Away*, E: Brokedown Palace

*W Stephen Stills
